# Mosquitto ACL — Topic access control
#
# esp32 user: can publish device readings only
# api user: can subscribe to all device readings
# admin user: full access for debugging

user esp32
topic write metabreath/+/reading
topic read metabreath/+/cmd

user api
topic read metabreath/+/reading
topic write metabreath/+/cmd

user admin
topic readwrite #
